          <span class="block text-[#E11D48] mt-2">PAGES</span>
          <span class="block mt-2">THAT</span>
          <span class="block text-[#E11D48] mt-2">CONVERT</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-700 font-medium leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mb-8">
          <span class="font-black text-[#E11D48]">Single focus. Zero distractions.</span> Framer builds stunning landing pages in 60 seconds.
          <span class="font-black text-gray-500">Durable adds lead capture with built-in CRM</span>.
          AI handles design, you optimize conversion.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <span class="bg-[#E11D48] text-white px-4 py-2 font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">High Converting</span>
